Here is the explanation of this diagram:


This diagram depicts

- Web Servers behind a Load Balancer. This helps to redistribute traffic to non too busy servers to balance load to prevent downtime and crash.
- Three Firewalls for security.
- An SSL Certificate for serving www.foobar.com over HTTPS.
- Three Monitoring Clients (Data Collectors) for Sumologic or other monitoring services.

The components are interconnected to illustrate the flow of data and traffic within the infrastructure.
